   854                                  NAMBAR_REG      equ     10h             ; native audio mixer BAR
   855                                   NAM_SIZE       equ     256             ; 256 bytes required.
   856                                  
   857                                  NABMBAR_REG     equ     14h             ; native audio bus mastering BAR
